370 570 Foreign ministers of member-states meeting in the Ethiopian capital agreed to set up a seven-member panel to investigate who shot down Rwandan President Juvenal Habyarimana 's plane on April 6 , 1994 .
571 751 The assassination touched off a murderous rampage by Hutu security forces and civilians , who slaughtered mainly Tutsis but also Hutus who favored reconciliation with the minority .
752 784 It also reignited the civil war .
785 941 The panel also will look at the exodus of about 2 million Rwanda Hutus to neighboring countries where they lived in U.N.-run refugee camps for 2Ê1\/2 years .
942 1180 The investigation will consider the role of `` internal and external forces prior to the genocide and subsequently , and the role of the United Nations and its agencies and the OAU before , during and after the genocide , '' the OAU said .
1181 1280 The panel will be based in Addis Ababa , and will finish its investigation within a year , it said .
1281 1365 It is to be funded by voluntary contributions from within and outside the continent .
